summary: Comprehensive testing of Coach Management System completed successfully. All major features working including coach profiles, targets, session linking, live observation, and AI summaries.

integration_issues.issue: AI summary generation takes longer than expected (10+ seconds), may need loading indicator improvement

passed_tests: Home page loads with My Coaches button
My Coaches page navigation and functionality
Coach profile creation with name and role
Coach profile tabs (Overview, Targets, Sessions) all accessible
Development targets can be added and managed
Session setup with coach selection dropdown working
Live observation starts and tracks ball rolling state
Event logging during live observation works
Session can be ended and navigates to review page
Session notes can be added and saved
Ball rolling tracking from session start (defaults to 'not rolling')
Unused session parts removed on session end
